      "title": "One person was killed in the firing",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person died in the firing that took place last night (3) in the Thalkaswala area of \u200b\u200bGalle, Pidgala.",
        "A 31-year-old man from Pidgala-Miagama region died in this way.",
        "The deceased was returning home in Unturuli after going to the city yesterday, when a shot was fired at him near the house. (a)"
